@union_cooperate

With the unions in control of the economy, it has become necessary to cooperate with them heavily in order to continue our economic recovery. With the CGdL in the industrial north and Federterra in the agricultural south, our policy with the respective trade unions must remain cordial.

- @improve_cgdl: Improve our relations with the CGdL.
- @improve_federterra: Improve our relations with Federterra.

